                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/1748" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OB-0126</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8461 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山东青岛中西医结合医院的重生历程</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Regeneration Course of the Qingdao Integrative Hospital of Traditional Chinese and Western Medic</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贺广明，栾贞增等</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">青岛大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山东青岛中西结合医院</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医药卫生工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中医院；组织变革；二次创业；医德；医院管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Traditional Chinese Medicine Hospital; organizational change; second venture; medical ethics; hospital management</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了山东青岛中西医结合医院置之死地而后生的重生历程。作为中医特色医院典型代表，本案例通过对该中医院艰难的重生历程叙述，刻画了中医特色医院普遍存在的生存困境、变革探索和二次创业历程。鉴于中国医院管理复杂而低效、患者满意度低的严峻形势，本案例不仅主题敏感而重要，案例开发方法也必须突破创新。案例开发者借鉴经验管理学派代表德鲁克先生的案例研究方法，深入该医院进行了一年多的观察、访谈、体验，特别是多次参加医院管理会议，以深层型案例开发模式突破了仅用几天时间进行访谈的浅表型案例开发模式，更深入、准确地把握了案例的本质。在案例故事叙述上大胆借鉴了诺贝尔文学奖获得者莫言的某些故事讲述方法，突出管理故事讲述的亲验性。并参考了社会各界关于医疗的观点，强化了多元思维和信息的丰富性。本案例对医改形势下中医院的生存与管理、变革与创新，以及社会医疗资源的合理配置等重大问题提供了深刻的思考素材。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes the process of the rebirth of the integrative medicine hospital of Qingdao in Shandong Province. As a typical representative of the special medicine hospital, this case depicts the plight of survival and the development challenges in the most of Chinese medicine hospitals. In the view of the complex and inefficient hospital management and the critical situation of health care reform, this case involves of sensitive topics and important contents, so it must also be a breakthrough in the innovation of the case development approaches. In the view of the specificity of this case , the case developers learns the approach of the Peter Drucker’s case study ,who is the representative of the practical management ,and then go into the hospital for nine months of observation, interview, experience and the management activities, especially in the hospital’s executive team meeting . With the deep case development activities mode, it breaks through the superficial case development mode in a few days for interview. In the way of telling story, the case developer draw some story descriptions from the Mo Yan, who has recently deserves the Nobel Prize. And the case writers, as an experienced manager identity, make use of a modern storyteller’s methods to tell the story of personal experiences of management. By the way of collecting, citing from all the social walks of life second-hand information about health, this case strengthens the abundant multi-thinking and information. This case provides a deep thinking material for the changes about the Chinese medicine hospitals’ survival, scientific management, the Chinese medicine’s development and innovation, and the rational allocation of medical resources of the society under the background of the Chinese hospital reform.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2013</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《领导学》、《组织行为学》、《人力资源管理》、《管理学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">组织变革</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2014-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
